<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von der red
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, die auf <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>
<expan>Erhart<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>Zeyrn<ex>er</ex></expan> gee, als von <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
                        knecht <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, <expan>gena<ex>n</ex>t</expan> die
                                <expan>hewffl<ex>er</ex></expan>, die er
                            <expan>gehalte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<add>und gelt von uns <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan></add> süll
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc., das
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol ver <expan>nome<ex>n</ex></expan>.
                        Und ist uns <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> niht
                            <expan>wissenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> und <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan> teils von dem
                            <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> Erhart
                            <expan>Zeyrn<ex>er</ex></expan> niht <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan> denn
                        guts. Denn wo wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>frewnts<ex>chaft</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        dienst etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
